com.facebook.buck.artifact_cache

Class ThriftArtifactCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.artifact_cache.AbstractAsynchronousCache
      • com.facebook.buck.artifact_cache.AbstractNetworkCache
        • com.facebook.buck.artifact_cache.ThriftArtifactCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArtifactCache, AutoCloseable

    public class ThriftArtifactCache
extends AbstractNetworkCache
    This is the Thrift protocol for the cache. The underlying channel is still HTTP but the payload is Thrift. To learn a bit more about the protocol please look at ThriftArtifactCacheProtocol.
